QuestData.Title: Hivekiller Stinger
QuestData.Description:
Wasps are a bee's natural enemy, and none are more deadly than this highly specialized killer. It will terrorize the hive no longer, thanks to you.
The Hivemother will be interested in this item.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Hivekiller Stinger to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take the Hivekiller Stinger to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
